Text:
"Two years after tens of thousands of demonstrators shut down the WTO meetings in Seattle, here's an audio introduction to the New World Order & its discontents. The double CD covers changing politics, militarism & policing; environmental issues, frankenfood & genetic engineering; digital capitalism & the fairy-tale economic boom and the leading alternatives to and struggles against a system which puts profits over people, unregulated growth over sustainability and money over morals."
